msgstr "`Os arquivos cacerts` devem ser adicionados ao `function.zip`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To do this, first create a directory `src/main/zip.native/` with your build.  Next create a shell script file called `bootstrap`\n"
